# simple-chat
Chat application using TCP

Requires:
Python 2.7
sudo apt-get install python (on Ubunutu)

Usage:

------SERVER------

python new_server.py [host_ip] [port] [server duration]
	EXAMPLE: python new_server.py 10.170.0.80 5003 1.2
Server script is now executed. No additional work needed.

------------------

------CLIENT------

python new_client.py [server_ip] [port]
	EXAMPLE: python new_client.py 10.170.0.80 5003

Enter username

**TYPE HELP FOR POSSIBLE COMMANDS**

From here you can enter one of the following commands to get started:
	list - lists all clients connected to the server
	all [MESSAGE] - sends message to all clients connected
	msg [CLIENT_NAME] [MESSAGE] - sends message to specified client only
	quit - quits the server

-------------------
